      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road with this reliable daily driver! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it still runs strong and is ready for many more miles. It's the perfect choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a great price point\u2014solid, dependable, and full of potential!",
