    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great, though there are a few minor surface scratches and small door dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid; it starts reliably, shifts smoothly, and has a complete service history. It\u2019s a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that\u2019s ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
