    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely flawless condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it still drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s super clean inside and out (no spills, no scratches!), and I\u2019m just looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. It's practically brand new and ready for a new home. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
