    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive folder of every service record performed exclusively at the dealership. It drives with the tight, responsive precision of a vehicle that just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast seeking a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle that has been pampered regardless of cost.",
      "price": 46500.0,
